Name: TLI (Concatinated)
checklistText:
<size=21>Concatinated Trans-Lunar Injection checklist</size>

Note:
Use the S-IVB burn planner to set up the burn before running P15.

This checklist is a concatinated and slightly simplified version of the other 3 checklists. Use this OR the other 3 in sequence to perform a TLI.

	XLUNAR - INJECT (verify)
Panel 7
	EDS PWR - on (up)
Panel 1
